    "The concept of future plans extends this idea further by utilizing an approximated model of the environment and the behavior models of other agents.",
    "This approach enables the generation of a sequence of possible future observations and actions [89].",
    "Such knowledge is shared among agents, allowing the receivers to consider the potential future outcomes of the senders' actions.",
    "Message combinationWhen agents receive more than one message, current works often aggregate all received messages to reduce the input for the action policy.",
